      <title>美国对中国黑客的最大担忧在关岛显现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-03/chinese-cyber-hackers-terrify-us-intelligence-after-infiltrating-guam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构称，太平洋偏远岛屿上的小型电信网络和公用设施正面临着中国前所未有的网络战计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-03/chinese-cyber-hackers-terrify-us-intelligence-after-infiltrating-guam</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 16:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对涉嫌僵尸网络攻击的中国网络公司实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/us-sanctions-chinese-cybersecutity-firm-linked-to-botnet-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部对中国网络安全公司 Integrity Technology Group 进行了制裁，原因是其涉嫌参与了国家支持的名为 Flax Typhoon 的僵尸网络攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/us-sanctions-chinese-cybersecutity-firm-linked-to-botnet-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 15:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登阻止新日铁以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/president-biden-blocks-nippon-steel-bid-for-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登阻​​止了美国钢铁公司以 141 亿美元的价格出售给新日本制铁公司的交易，从而终止了这项引发政治风暴和美日紧张关系的备受瞩目的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/president-biden-blocks-nippon-steel-bid-for-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 13:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲试图与叙利亚建立联系并削弱普京的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/europe-aims-to-build-ties-with-syria-s-leaders-to-cut-putin-s-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和法国外交部长访问大马士革，欧盟加大力度与叙利亚新领导人建立联系，并说服他们减少俄罗斯对这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/europe-aims-to-build-ties-with-syria-s-leaders-to-cut-putin-s-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦调查局警告伊斯兰国可能利用新奥尔良袭击事件的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/new-orleans-attack-shows-enduring-influence-of-islamic-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社获得的评估显示，美国官员警告称，伊斯兰国将试图利用新年新奥尔良致命袭击事件引发更多暴力行为，尽管他们表示没有迹象表明该组织指挥了此次事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/new-orleans-attack-shows-enduring-influence-of-islamic-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 22:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房利美和房地美股价创五年新高，计划“最终解禁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-treasury-wins-back-key-role-in-fannie-mae-freddie-mac-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[抵押贷款巨头房利美和房地美的监管机构制定了解除政府监管的路线图，导致这两家实体的普通股股价升至 2019 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-treasury-wins-back-key-role-in-fannie-mae-freddie-mac-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 21:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
